HEADWORD: Assish
<hw>Ass"ish</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling an ass;
asinine; stupid or obstinate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Such . . . appear to be of the <qex>assich</qex> kind . . . </q>
